Description :
        When I was young, was my heart toward you love or friendship? No, maybe it wasn't love or friendship, but jealousy toward you. Baek Ho-jin, a national judo player who has never felt the feeling of endless decline, Choi Jeong-won, a magazine editor who is on the verge of being fired for an outspoken interview, a piece of memory that passes before him, a high school classmate and the hottest national hero in Korea. He must get an interview with Baek Ho-jin, but will Jeong-won be able to succeed in the interview and survive at the company? BACK STAGE Last story
